<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,viewport-fit=cover,maximum-scale=5">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"><meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#1a3a4a"><meta name="color-scheme" content="light">
<title>Interkulturelle Kommunikation — China trifft Deutschland</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,500;0,700;1,500&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--blau:#1a3a4a;--rot:#c1121f;--gold:#d4a348;--gold-light:#fdf6e3;--sand:#f4efe6;--papier:#f7f3eb;--weiß:#fdfdfc;--grau:#4a4a4a;--grau-light:#7a7a7a;--linie:#ccc0ad;--linie-fein:#e0d8cc;--china-red:#b83030;--shadow-sm:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06);--shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.08);--shadow-lg:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);--radius:6px;--radius-lg:12px;--ease:cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);--ease-bounce:cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);--safe-top:env(safe-area-inset-top,0px);--safe-bottom:env(safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:clamp(15px,1.4vw,19px);background:var(--sand)}
body{font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;color:var(--blau);line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-size-adjust:100%}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.de{font-style:normal}.zh{font-size:.82em;color:var(--grau-light);font-weight:400;font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif}.accent{color:var(--rot)}.gold{color:var(--gold)}.china{color:var(--china-red)}
#progress-bar{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blau),var(--china-red),var(--gold));z-index:1000;transition:width .5s var(--ease)}
#progress-dots{position:fixed;top:14px;right:24px;display:flex;gap:6px;z-index:999}
#progress-dots .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--linie);cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s var(--ease)}
#progress-dots .dot.active{background:var(--china-red);transform:scale(1.4);box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(184,48,48,.4)}
#progress-dots .dot.done{background:var(--gold)}
.section{min-height:100vh;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:60px 20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.section.active{display:flex}
.section-inner{max-width:960px;width:100%;background:var(--weiß);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);padding:56px 48px;position:relative;z-index:1;border:1px solid var(--linie-fein)}
.section-tag{position:absolute;top:-14px;left:28px;font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 16px;border-radius:20px}
.section-tag.dark{background:var(--blau);color:var(--weiß)}.section-tag.red{background:var(--china-red);color:var(--weiß)}.section-tag.gold{background:var(--gold);color:var(--blau)}
.nav-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:36px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--linie-fein)}
.nav-btn{font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;background:var(--blau);color:var(--weiß);border:none;padding:11px 28px;border-radius:var(--radius);cursor:pointer;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.3px;transition:all .25s var(--ease)}
.nav-btn:hover{background:var(--china-red);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.nav-btn:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.nav-btn.prev{background:transparent;color:var(--grau);border:1px solid var(--linie);font-weight:400}
.nav-btn.prev:hover{background:var(--sand);border-color:var(--grau);color:var(--blau)}
.nav-btn.outline{background:transparent;color:var(--blau);border:1px solid var(--linie);font-weight:400;font-size:.85rem;padding:8px 18px}
.nav-btn.outline:hover{border-color:var(--china-red);color:var(--china-red)}
/* S1 COVER */#s1{background:var(--sand)}#s1 .section-inner{text-align:center;padding:64px 48px;max-width:800px}
#s1 .masthead{font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:32px;border:1px solid rgba(212,163,72,.3);padding:8px 28px;display:inline-block}
#s1 .headline{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5.5vw,4.2rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:12px}
#s1 .headline .hl-china{color:var(--china-red);position:relative}#s1 .headline .hl-germany{color:var(--blau)}
#s1 .subhead{font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--grau);margin-bottom:24px}
#s1 .dek{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--grau-light);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.7}
#s1 .culture-strip{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-top:40px}
#s1 .culture-strip span{width:36px;height:3px}#s1 .culture-strip .black{background:var(--blau)}#s1 .culture-strip .red{background:var(--china-red)}#s1 .culture-strip .gold{background:var(--gold)}
/* S2 TEXT MANFRED */.text-block{padding:20px 24px;background:var(--sand);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border-left:4px solid var(--gold);font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:2;margin-top:16px}
.text-block .vocab-word{color:var(--china-red);font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px dashed var(--gold);padding:0 2px;transition:all .2s}
.text-block .vocab-word:hover{background:var(--gold-light);border-radius:3px}
.text-zh{font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--grau-light);margin-top:16px;padding:16px 20px;background:var(--weiß);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);line-height:1.8;display:none}
.text-zh.show{display:block;animation:slideIn .4s var(--ease)}
@keyframes slideIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
/* S3 TEXT GABRIELA */.text-tabs{display:flex;gap:0;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--linie-fein)}
.text-tab{padding:10px 24px;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:transparent;font-size:.88rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--grau-light);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:all .25s;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-2px}
.text-tab.active{color:var(--china-red);border-bottom-color:var(--china-red);font-weight:600}
.text-tab:hover{color:var(--blau)}
.text-person{display:none;animation:slideIn .35s var(--ease)}
.text-person.active{display:block}
/* VOCAB PANEL */.vocab-panel{display:none;position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:var(--weiß);border-radius:20px 20px 0 0;box-shadow:0 -8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.15);padding:28px 24px 32px;z-index:2000;max-height:45vh;overflow-y:auto;animation:slideUp .35s var(--ease)}
.vocab-panel.show{display:block}
@keyframes slideUp{from{transform:translateY(100%)}to{transform:none}}
.vocab-panel .vp-word{font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blau);margin-bottom:4px}
.vocab-panel .vp-zh{font-size:1rem;color:var(--china-red);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif}
.vocab-panel .vp-example{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--grau);padding:10px 14px;background:var(--sand);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.6}
.vocab-panel .vp-close{position:absolute;top:12px;right:16px;font-size:1.4rem;cursor:pointer;color:var(--grau-light);background:none;border:none;padding:4px 8px}
.vocab-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);z-index:1999}
.vocab-overlay.show{display:block}
/* S4 WORD CLOUD CATEGORIES */.cat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:20px}
.cat-card{background:var(--sand);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:20px;border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);transition:all .3s var(--ease)}
.cat-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)}
.cat-card h4{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--blau)}
.cat-card .cat-word{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--linie-fein);font-size:.85rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.cat-card .cat-word:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.cat-card .cat-word:hover{color:var(--china-red)}
.cat-card .cat-word .cw-de{font-weight:500}.cat-card .cat-word .cw-zh{color:var(--grau-light);font-size:.8rem}
/* S5 GRAMMAR */.grammar-card{background:var(--weiß);border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:24px;margin-top:14px;transition:all .3s var(--ease);cursor:pointer}
.grammar-card:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow);border-color:var(--gold)}
.grammar-card .gc-title{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blau);margin-bottom:6px}
.grammar-card .gc-marker{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--grau-light);font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}
.grammar-card .gc-example{font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:.95rem;padding:12px 16px;background:var(--sand);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-top:10px;line-height:1.7;display:none}
.grammar-card .gc-example.show{display:block;animation:slideIn .3s var(--ease)}
/* S6 FLIP CARDS */.flip-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(145px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-top:20px}
.flip-card{perspective:900px;height:145px}
.flip-card-inner{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;transition:transform .5s var(--ease);transform-style:preserve-3d;cursor:pointer}
.flip-card.flipped .flip-card-inner{transform:rotateY(180deg)}
.flip-card-front,.flip-card-back{position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;backface-visibility:hidden;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);padding:8px;text-align:center}
.flip-card-front{background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--weiß),#f0f4f8);gap:4px}
.flip-card-front .fc-de{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blau)}
.flip-card-back{background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--china-red),#8a2020);color:var(--weiß);transform:rotateY(180deg);border:none}
.flip-card-back .fc-zh{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif}
.flip-card-back .fc-hint{font-size:.7rem;opacity:.7;margin-top:4px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
/* S7 STRATEGIES MATCH */.strategy-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0;margin-top:20px}
.strat-left,.strat-right{padding:8px}
.strat-left .sl-item,.strat-right .sr-item{padding:10px 14px;margin:4px 0;border-radius:var(--radius);font-size:.85rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;border:2px solid transparent}
.strat-left .sl-item{background:var(--sand);border-color:var(--linie-fein)}
.strat-left .sl-item:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.strat-left .sl-item.selected{background:var(--gold-light);border-color:var(--gold)}
.strat-left .sl-item.matched{background:#d4edda;border-color:#28a745;opacity:.7}
.strat-right .sr-item{background:var(--weiß);border-color:var(--linie-fein);text-align:center}
.strat-right .sr-item:hover{background:#f0f4f8}
.strat-right .sr-item.matched{background:#d4edda;border-color:#28a745;opacity:.7}
.strat-match-status{text-align:center;margin-top:16px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--grau-light)}
/* S8 TYPICAL */.trait-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:16px}
.trait-col{padding:20px;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:var(--sand)}
.trait-col h4{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:1rem;text-align:center}
.trait-col .trait-tag{display:inline-block;padding:5px 14px;margin:4px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.82rem;background:var(--weiß);border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s}
.trait-col .trait-tag:hover{background:var(--gold-light);border-color:var(--gold)}
.trait-col .trait-tag.tagged{background:var(--blau);color:var(--weiß);border-color:var(--blau)}
.trait-col.china h4{color:var(--china-red)}.trait-col.germany h4{color:var(--blau)}
/* S9 TRANSLATION */.trans-card{padding:20px 24px;background:var(--sand);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);margin-top:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;border:2px solid var(--linie-fein)}
.trans-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)}
.trans-card .tc-cn{font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--blau);font-weight:500}
.trans-card .tc-de{display:none;font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--china-red);margin-top:8px;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--weiß);border-radius:var(--radius);line-height:1.7}
.trans-card .tc-de.show{display:block;animation:slideIn .35s var(--ease)}
.trans-card .tc-hint{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--grau-light);margin-top:6px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
/* S10 SCHLUSS */
#s10{background:var(--sand)}#s10 .section-inner{text-align:center;max-width:700px}
#s10 .final-quote{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3.5vw,2.4rem);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:16px}
#s10 .final-zh{font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--grau);margin-bottom:28px}
#s10 .culture-strip{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:0;margin-top:32px}
#s10 .culture-strip span{width:40px;height:2px}
#s10 .culture-strip .black{background:var(--blau)}#s10 .culture-strip .red{background:var(--china-red)}#s10 .culture-strip .gold{background:var(--gold)}
/* S11 VERGLEICH */
.compare-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:16px;font-size:.95rem}
.compare-table th,.compare-table td{padding:14px 16px;text-align:left;border:1px solid var(--linie-fein);vertical-align:top}
.compare-table th{background:var(--blau);color:var(--weiß);font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}
.compare-table .cat-zeit{background:#e8f4e8}.compare-table .cat-vor{background:#fdf2e9}.compare-table .cat-nach{background:#eaf2f8}
.compare-table .highlight{color:var(--china-red);font-weight:600}
.compare-table .example{font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.5;color:var(--grau)}
.compare-table .zh-ex{font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--grau-light);display:block;margin-top:4px}
#s10 .final-quote{font-family:'Playfair Display','Noto Sans SC',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3.5vw,2.4rem);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:16px}
#s10 .final-zh{font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--grau);margin-bottom:28px}
#s10 .culture-strip{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:0;margin-top:32px}
#s10 .culture-strip span{width:40px;height:2px}
#s10 .culture-strip .black{background:var(--blau)}#s10 .culture-strip .red{background:var(--china-red)}#s10 .culture-strip .gold{background:var(--gold)}
/* TOAST */.toast{position:fixed;bottom:32px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--blau);color:var(--weiß);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:30px;font-size:.88rem;z-index:3000;opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s;pointer-events:none;font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg)}.toast.show{opacity:1}
.key-hint{position:fixed;bottom:24px;left:24px;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--grau-light);z-index:998;opacity:.6;font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',sans-serif}
/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:479px){
  html{font-size:15px}.section{min-height:100dvh;padding:calc(var(--safe-top)+8px) 12px calc(var(--safe-bottom)+16px)}
  .section-inner{padding:28px 16px;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}.section-tag{top:-10px;left:16px;font-size:.65rem;padding:3px 12px;letter-spacing:2px}
  .section-inner h2{font-size:1.2rem}.nav-row{margin-top:24px;padding-top:14px;gap:10px;flex-direction:column}
  .nav-btn{padding:10px 20px;font-size:.82rem;min-height:44px}
  .flip-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px}.flip-card{height:130px}
  .flip-card-front .fc-de{font-size:.85rem}.flip-card-back .fc-zh{font-size:.9rem}
  .cat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px}.strategy-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0}
  .trait-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px}
  #s1 .headline{font-size:1.8rem}#s1 .subhead{font-size:.95rem}
  #progress-dots{top:calc(var(--safe-top)+8px);right:10px;gap:4px}#progress-dots .dot{width:7px;height:7px}
  .key-hint{display:none}.text-tabs{overflow-x:auto}.text-tab{padding:8px 14px;font-size:.82rem;white-space:nowrap}
}
@media(min-width:480px) and (max-width:767px){
  html{font-size:15.5px}.section{min-height:100dvh;padding:calc(var(--safe-top)+16px) 16px calc(var(--safe-bottom)+24px)}
  .section-inner{padding:32px 22px;border-radius:10px}.section-inner h2{font-size:1.3rem}
  .nav-btn{min-height:44px}.nav-row{flex-direction:column}
  .flip-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px}.flip-card{height:135px}
  .cat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px}
  .trait-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px}.key-hint{display:none}
}
@media(min-width:768px) and (max-width:1023px){
  .section{padding:50px 24px}.section-inner{padding:44px 36px}
  .flip-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
  .cat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}#s1 .headline{font-size:2.8rem}
}
@media(min-width:1024px) and (max-width:1439px){
  .section-inner{max-width:880px;padding:52px 48px}
  .flip-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr)}.cat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
}
@media(min-width:1440px){
  html{font-size:18px}.section{padding:60px 40px}.section-inner{max-width:1100px;padding:64px 64px;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl)}
  .section-tag{top:-16px;left:36px;font-size:.75rem;padding:6px 20px;letter-spacing:3px}
  .section-inner h2{font-size:1.8rem}.flip-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:16px}.flip-card{height:160px}
  .cat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px}.trait-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px}
  #s1 .headline{font-size:4.2rem}#s1 .subhead{font-size:1.4rem}
  .text-block{font-size:1.1rem;line-height:2.1}
}
@media(hover:none) and (pointer:coarse){.flip-card,.grammar-card,.trans-card,.cat-card .cat-word,.trait-tag{cursor:default}.nav-btn:active{transform:scale(.97)}}
@media print{.section{display:block!important;min-height:auto;page-break-after:always;padding:20px 0}
  #progress-bar,#progress-dots,.key-hint,.nav-row,.toast,.vocab-panel,.vocab-overlay{display:none!important}.section-inner{box-shadow:none;border:1px solid #ccc}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="progress-bar"></div><div id="progress-dots"></div><div id="toast" class="toast"></div><div class="key-hint">← → 翻页 | 点击交互</div>
<div class="vocab-overlay" id="vocabOverlay" onclick="closeVocabPanel()"></div>
<div class="vocab-panel" id="vocabPanel"><button class="vp-close" onclick="closeVocabPanel()">✕</button><div class="vp-word" id="vpWord"></div><div class="vp-zh" id="vpZh"></div><div class="vp-example" id="vpEx"></div></div>

<!-- S1 COVER -->
<section class="section active" id="s1" data-index="0">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="masthead">Kulturbrücke — Interkulturelle Kommunikation</div>
<h1 class="headline"><span class="hl-china">China</span> trifft <span class="hl-germany">Deutschland</span></h1>
<p class="subhead">Kulturen verstehen · Brücken bauen</p>
<p class="dek">两种文化的相遇并不总是一帆风顺。理解差异，学会适应，<br>是通向真正交流的第一步。</p>
<div class="culture-strip"><span class="black"></span><span class="red"></span><span class="gold"></span><span class="red"></span><span class="black"></span></div>
</div>
<div class="nav-row" style="position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);border:none;margin:0;padding:0;width:auto">
